title: Inspector Rex S02E25- Telephone Terror
description:
Inspector Rex S2 Ep25 - Telephone Terror

Kurt Bandisch sells antique toys in various Viennese locations. He obtains the phone numbers of female customers and begins to stalk and terrorise them over the phone. One woman is killed soon after receiving one of these terrifying calls. Can Brandtner and Rex find the suspect before he strikes again? Stars Gedeon Burkhard, Heinz Weixelbraun and Gerhard Ziemann. 

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
